works.description: Everybody likes to know about a celebrity’s crib. Numerous celebs earn a living and spend it on getting really lavish, luxurious homes. These homes have anything ranging from a highly expensive Olympic size swimming pool, copious rooms designated for arbitrary purposes, a deck, and a personalized helipad. One can’t even imagine what most of the worldly comforts are present in these palace-like houses. So, below are some mansions which are lavish in design and belong to some of the world’s most prevalent stars.
